{
  "stem": "27767.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and we didn't have too much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had in other places.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like when I went to [ROMANIAN], to Cluj, that-- when they-- you know, they came after me or they tried to-- to hit me, or whatever, you know?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and screaming, 'Jew,' 'dirty Jew,' whatever, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was between '40 and '44.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The kehillah, it was-- the Jewish kehillah was-- it was an Orthodox kehillah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a nice synagogue, a pretty big one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the women were upstairs and-- and the men downstairs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[COUGHS] They had the ritual bath in the-- [COUGHS] --in the yard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went to, every morning and evening-- actually, we went to school, we couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We went-- they woke us up early morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went to the cheder to-- we were down there in the morning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we went to school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The public-- the public school started at 8 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they woke us up about 6 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we went to-- as young little children, we went to the cheder.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the cheder, we--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only the boys, not the girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from there, we went to the school, and until 1 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "School was from 8:00 to 1:00.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at 1 o'clock, we went home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everybody was eating lunch.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Lunch was the main, the main course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was the dinner, actually, at 1 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And everybody was sitting down to the table, the children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My father, if he was out in the-- in the forest-- he went out sometimes 20 miles or 10 miles, you know, to work.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he had his job-- or when he wasn't in the store.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So otherwise, everybody was eating at 1 o'clock together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had lunch.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And at 2 o'clock, we went-- I went to the cheder back.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
